cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MA 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with the design of a UAV relay network for wireless communication, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper deals with the trajectory optimization of a rotary-wing UAV, which falls under the scope of robotics. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the optimization of communication delay and power consumption, which falls under the scope of information theory. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the design of a semi-Markov decision process for trajectory optimization, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
5. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with the optimization of a UAV relay network, which can be considered a multiagent system.
